main event: Two observers sighted a green round object and multiple bright elliptical objects near Minden, Nebraska in 1968.
interesting points: The observers first saw a green object clearly while driving,They noticed another object that appeared to be a plane but was actually several separate bright objects,The bright objects emitted a loud noise resembling a sharp pocket burst when they separated,The green ball sighted earlier was speculated to be connected to the later sighting,No physical evidence or photographs were available in the report.
sighted object: green round object and bright elliptical objects
witness description: a couple driving over the Interstate-80 Bridge
